  "texts": [
    "Result discussionWe tested our two GPT industrial bot versions operations in four case studies: an auto-parameters configuration for a PLC and a SCADA system in an I5.0 context (adding the I5.0 print to an existing I4.0 model), a faulty equipment discovery, a root cause analysis, and a synthetic data generation feature.",
    "On the one hand, the offline GPT industrial chatbot we designed is more secure than the online version since the customized factory data is not exposed to the World Wide Web or OpenAI.",
    "The loaded data remains a property of the local factory server while using GPT-4 LM services through APIs and Langchain agents.",
    "Therefore, it is suitable for factories dealing with sensitive data.",
    "On the other hand, the offline version only responds to straightforward queries and is exclusively boxed to the customized data loaded."
  ],
